{"tid":989812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人瑞永別】全球最長壽男性睡夢中離世 享年113歲","createTime":"2019-01-21T06:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T15:52:54.000Z","uid":130626,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"76ae2bd952044a78b6583fed1c608666c9824fbf","tid":989812,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:54:57.000Z","msg":"去年被確認為全球最長壽男士、居住在日本北海道的野中正造，今天凌晨在家中逝世，享年113歲。<br />\n野中正造於1905年7月25日出生，去年4月被健力士世界紀錄確認為全球最長壽男性。野中平日要靠輪椅代步，亦需要人輔助。但去年7月家人為他開生日會時，他仍能一口氣吹熄蛋糕上的蠟燭，精神不錯。<br />\n據悉野中去世前一切如常，過世前一天仍照常進食三餐，但家人今天凌晨1時半左右發現他在睡夢中離開。野中在北海道足寄町經營溫泉旅館，家人稱他閒時喜歡泡溫泉。<br />\n他的孫女祐子說︰「失去了重要的人打擊很大，他平靜離世沒有為家人帶來不安。雖然我們曾多次吵架，但相處仍很快樂，我心中充滿感激之情。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190120/large/1547996438_a039.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F1547996438_a039.jpg&h=51be6382&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b75c354b5b8d722044b8687f0e63c57ce691ad0d","tid":989812,"uid":157193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:57:18.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25417983625cb3c6beb018829708c6b275ab1bb","tid":989812,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:59:23.000Z","msg":"廢老"},{"pid":"86ed1fb029a322d2feb71da949ccf4daccf9e613","tid":989812,"uid":74908,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:59:48.000Z","msg":"冇120歲做唔係60歲中年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229f2f2906c8f7a7166caa038f235f4a16ae1d36","tid":989812,"uid":64374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:00:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8b06eda8c6938f9057eb5d36e060371a265bc41","tid":989812,"uid":54337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:00:35.000Z","m